All Known Implementing Classes:
CompressedNamesIndex, LoadableSignalDatabaseImpl, SignalDatabaseImpl, SimulationCompressedUWI, SimulationHSpiceAscii, SimulationHSpiceCSDF, SimulationNonCompressedUWI, SimulationPsfAscii, SimulationPsfAsciiDC
public interface NamesIndex
extends MetaInfo

SimulationOutputHeader provides a view on the names and units that exist in a simulation output file. Each signal is associated with a unique index, which should be matched with the index in SimulationOutputBody (and in the file itself ).

Author:
scoseman
